After adding the tool definition, run `npm run generate:browser-tools-catalog` to regenerate `platform/shared/src/generated/browser-tools-catalog.ts`. This script reads the compiled browser tools and writes a static catalog. The build will fail if the catalog is out of sync with the definitions.

